Problem Statement

Demographics are a key part of your small business marketing strategy. Demographics help you identify and segment the individual members of your audience by key characteristics, wants and needs . Demographics make your marketing efforts more effective, and it is the  key element for running a successful marketing campaign. According to the Statista, 36.6 percent of women in the United States had completed four years or more of college in 2019 which is Up from 3.8 percent of women in 1940. Also, 35.4 percent of males in US have completed four years or more of college which is up from 5.5 percent in 1940.
